pageContext.claim: “I had another poll that -- and CNN didn't want to use it, so they used another poll where mostly Democrats were polled. Take a look at who they're polling, if they poll anybody, because I don't even think they go out and poll. I think they sit at a desk and say, give this number, give that number.”
pageContext.analysis: News and polling organizations do not publish fake polls and articles about those polls often include interviews with named participants.
